code: static CamelContext getCamelContextById(BeanManager manager, String camelContextId) {     Bean<?> bean = manager.resolve(manager.getBeans(camelContextId)).     return (CamelContext) manager.getReference(bean, CamelContext.class, manager.createCreationalContext(bean)). }

static CamelContext getDefaultCamelContext(BeanManager manager) {     Bean<?> bean = manager.resolve(manager.getBeans(CamelContext.class)).     return (CamelContext) manager.getReference(bean, CamelContext.class, manager.createCreationalContext(bean)). }
